snippet.title: Among Us but it's Star Wars
snippet.description:
Hello there! As requested, a brand new Among Us / Star Wars animation is finally here! Witness the greatest lightsaber duels in Star Wars history recreated in Among Us animation! And thread carefully -- someone is the impostor!
Like, comment, and subscribe :)
Subscribe here: https://www.youtube.com/user/nchldmn/...
